{"tid":322883,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩記帳app好用？","createTime":"2017-07-15T07:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T11:27:43.000Z","uid":99896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4a76656360fdb88169bc3abbe3feed07896a8f69","tid":322883,"uid":99896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:39:19.000Z","msg":"本身用緊Ahorro用左年幾，但係佢只有app版，有時想用電腦edit下<br />\n<br />\n係隔離post個整合見到呢幾隻app:<br />\nMoney Manager Next - Expense &amp; Budget - 唔同account, 唔同category 計budget都有<br />\nMoney Pro<br />\nMoneyWiz<br />\nMoze - 記帳，彈指之間<br />\n秒速記帳 1SecMoney<br />\n隨手記 - 雖然係大陸app, 可以自訂支出同埋budget 的分類sub分類，仲可以set係咩信用卡銀行戶口<br />\n圈子帳本<br />\nWeple Money Pro - 簡單，快<br />\n<br />\n我自己查過Money Manager Next 好似只有mac版，有啲又冇得pc edit<br />\n想問下有冇人用過呢幾隻app or 其他，可以pc+app 同步 edit<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a57a02f5ba3488c03dc0c1d2e6251976ddac5ce","tid":322883,"uid":82279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:50:34.000Z","msg":"Freshbook"},{"pid":"4338bd4058083022b1524b1721b4b19975b2e735","tid":322883,"uid":896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:50:35.000Z","msg":"用緊隻N 年前o既 YNAB 4 (新果隻行佢自己個雲端, 不過無得買斷)<br />\n隻 YNAB4 有 PC + App, 經 Dropbox 做同步<br />\n可以set on/off budget account, categories (also sub-cat), report 分析<br />\nOver/under budget 可以自選帶唔帶去下個月"},{"pid":"1dd9736792ed34e87716a6cb6697f6873138f9de","tid":322883,"uid":3122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:55:25.000Z","msg":"Excel"},{"pid":"e9ea8bbebd2a2f65f65edf09061f62fc991bbaf0","tid":322883,"uid":20865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:06:16.000Z","msg":"Moneywiz 有齊android iOS Mac windows"},{"pid":"75b51de47c6c9887208c3f35a266b6c480fbf8db","tid":322883,"uid":44220,"like":0,"dislike":0